{
  "stem": "734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at that point, I was already-- I mean, everybody was really up and around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we already-- I mean, we knew and I-- probably with my nine English words, I was going to be the interpreter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And everybody-- Sasha and Andre and-- everybody was already at the gate, waiting for them when came around, the two tanks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the first thing I know is the turret opens up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there's this man with goggles and a helmet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you can imagine what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The gate is closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this is all barb wire, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, we can see through it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean there's visibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he must have been the head-- the, I know he had a bar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a lieutenant maybe or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says-- the first thing he says is, who are you, what is this?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What camp is this, who are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to him what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then another tank is, appears in this second reconnaissance tank.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the, the driver sticks his head out on the front, through this, through that hatch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He opened the hatch, and he sticks his head out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His face is all dark from smog or smudge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sort of-- and at some point, while I am engaged talking to him, trying to explain-- not talking, really.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Trying-- between my French and the few English words that I knew, I tell him what it's-- what it is and what we are doing here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that, and I said to him, lots of sickness, I said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Lots of sickness, epidemics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this fellow from the other tank looks at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was sort of closer to the gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
